snippet.title: How Culture Wars and White Supremacy Go Together Like “Green Eggs and Ham” | The Amber Ruffin Show
snippet.description:
The Amber Ruffin Show. Streaming on Peacock https://pck.tv/3pOiao8
Reserve your spot in the live studio audience for The Amber Ruffin Show at https://1iota.com/show/1210/the-amber-ruffin-show

If it seems like politicians spend more time these days talking about Aunt Jemima getting taken off pancake mix, and who can use what bathroom than they spend on domestic terrorism, voter suppression, and raising minimum wage, it’s only because you are absolutely correct.

In the last year, there’s been one discussion in Congress on raising the minimum wage, and it only lasted two hours and seven minutes. Meanwhile, there have been 14 hours of congressional testimony on “cancel culture.” If you’re wondering how we got here, maybe Amber can help in a segment called, “How Did We Get Here?”

Show Synopsis: Amber showcases her signature smart-and-silly take on the news of the week, responding to it all with a charming, late-night mix of seriousness, nonsense, and evening gowns.
